name: Arsène Lupin
ability: Moderately increases the number of soulstones received from battle and slightly increases battle reward drop rate.

additional_data.description: The spirit of a thief so famous everyone knows his name. He used to break into safes and vaults in his spare time, but now he's grown a bit bored of it all. His new plan is to travel the lands stealing not from humans, but from nature.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ Limited Jewel Summon 21/09/16 - 12/10/16
◦ Trade at Exchange for 70 Mochi 09/10/16 - 12/10/16
additional_data.notes_and_trivia:
◦ Increases the Skill DMG of all allies by 25% during the "Jewels and The Secret Workshop" event.
◦ Summon rate increased until 21/09/16 - 12/10/16

main: "That old box was your safe? My goodness! You should be more careful!"
skill: "You shall know the pain of losing something precious to you."
summon: "You want my help? Very well! Just show me which lock needs cracking."
limit_break: "Who knows what locks and boxes await me next..."
